https://wpguru.co.uk/2016/11/how-to-boot-centos-7-into-command-line-or-gui-mode/

Turns out, this is just another system service.

yes, master> sudo systemctl set-default multi-user.target

If you want to change the default back to GUI:

yes, master> sudo systemctl set-default graphical.target
